“Tinkalye kwene chitela cha Zakkum.”
“Ni tinkachigumbasyeje ndumbo (syenu).”
“Ni tinkachimweleje mesi gamasemule nnope.”
“Ni tinkamweje mwasikumwelaga ngamiya syanjota nnope.”
